{"tid":2185221,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［感同身受］曾捲三角戀婚外情傳聞 謝安琪留言俾心撐細So！！！","createTime":"2020-09-02T06:25:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T13:21:48.000Z","uid":56716,"like":32,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"bbfbd8604f898b9ea73ee8e9c42e44045c8ddb4d","tid":2185221,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T06:25:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/etSZTdh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FetSZTdh.png&h=399a0b58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">Kay:I know that feel bro！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n溫故知新1<br />\n謝安琪與張繼聰當年一同就讀大埔恩主教書院，身為籃球隊萬人迷的張繼聰，一早就吸引了師姐謝安琪的注意，但當時女方很自卑，直至畢業也沒敢主動表白。畢業後，張繼聰考進演藝學院，謝安琪則在香港大學主修美國研究，二人不時有聯絡聚會。謝安琪讀大學時因參加歌唱表演而認識經紀人周博賢，畢業後當了一年鋼琴教師，便正式隨周博賢加入樂壇，與張繼聰見面機會愈來愈多，隨後共墜愛河。張繼聰為此與拍拖7年的演藝學院師妹梁嘉琪分手。<br />\n<br />\n溫故知新2<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fVO2Q0F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfVO2Q0F.jpg&h=2d2aa479&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jbhryd1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjbhryd1.jpg&h=af5f52a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b13834d31e43fcc2eeffd3fee92de1b700b21923","tid":2185221,"uid":122167,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T06:38:25.000Z","msg":"搶111"},{"pid":"6a73f262d235eb766a290db29839dfa957c14ed7","tid":2185221,"uid":219398,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T06:49:07.000Z","msg":"淫k同佢可能都黎過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce666abcdc8b0c4e48b86cd5b0a5877bc4a5e7bc","tid":2185221,"uid":4780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T06:56:27.000Z","msg":"阿B = 仁K<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b5efd